{"tid":1040091,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙利說道：「我對全隊的一條信息：我們是一個團隊，而不是25」","createTime":"2019-02-28T00:09:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T03:41:38.000Z","uid":36372,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce4773f3d0599d3fdd076698ae77546a079abc8f","tid":1040091,"uid":36372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T00:09:54.000Z","msg":"新浪網<br />\n<br />\n沙利:艾利沙巴拿加後備是我的選擇 給車路士傳達一個信息<br />\n新浪網 2019-02-28 06:22:40  <br />\n<br />\n艾利沙巴拿加今場失去了正選<br />\n　　在本輪英超的一場焦點大戰中，坐鎮主場的車路士2-0擊敗熱刺，拿下了一場關鍵的勝利。今場比賽除了結果外，另一個引人關注的問題就是車路士對門將艾利沙巴拿加的處理，由於在聯賽盃決賽上拒絕被換下，艾利沙巴拿加被車路士罰款一週薪水，今場對熱刺的比賽，艾利沙巴拿加也被卡巴尼路拿走了正選位置。賽後，沙利認為這個做法傳遞了自己想要表達的信息。<br />\n<br />\n　　在接受BT體育採訪時，沙利說道：「這是個選擇，也是我對全隊的一條信息：我們是一個團隊，而不是25個獨立的球員。」"},{"pid":"c7db59be5bc438c2d42f9c5d5eac8fac7e28efce","tid":1040091,"uid":36372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T00:48:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7802ceffed2fac7fa97f32c3666469e647054740","tid":1040091,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:19:31.000Z","msg":"25 out <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf64fbf7ac3bb08736807f47de9d2880bbbab291","tid":1040091,"uid":36372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30776a50d0974d29a2aa645126c8bf611efa72a2","tid":1040091,"uid":19889,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:29:13.000Z","msg":"屌你又cut得幾靚"},{"pid":"7afdbefb3bc23bfc73ba146e05a9c79251b36164","tid":1040091,"uid":7940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:34:15.000Z","msg":"又抽古圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb21459fc3c752cc0989c36e71d9c5b4f33801d9","tid":1040091,"uid":2559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T